      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKOTA COURTNEY (2) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (22.78) behind Savvy Lad at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. MR. SPECKLE (8) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Grade 5 winner two back at Gunnedah. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to bounce back to best. DRINK ROSE (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (22.68) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Expected to feature. MISS BANSKY (7) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
